        {
          "text": "The name \"Vexana\" may comes from the Latin word \"vexare,\" which means to torment, distress, or harass. This could symbolize her ability to curse, harm, and control enemies through her necromantic powers, fitting her role as a necromancer who manipulates the spirits of the dead and inflicts torment on her foes.",
