            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "Her scepter belongs to Duke Atticus her fiance, Whom had corrupted on their supposed wedding day"
        },
        {
          "text": "The souls of Atticus and brave fighters are present in undead knight"
        },
        {
          "text": "In Project NEXT, a major update aimed at reworking and balancing older heroes in Mobile Legends: Bang Bang, Vexana was one of the heroes revamped alongside several others.",
