        {
          "text": "Vexana is the first hero to receive a Zenith-grade skin in Mobile Legends: Bang Bang. Her \"Twisted Fairytale\" skin, introduced between March 25 and April 30, 2024, marked the debut of this high-rarity skin category. Currently, Vexana and are the only heroes with Zenith skin.",
